external_knowledge:
A "rise to fame" refers to a significant increase in reputation in the game; 
The "sharpest rise" means the largest total reputation gain; 
The "top 5 players" refers to the players with the highest total reputation gain, ranked in descending order.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT p.player_name
FROM players p
INNER JOIN player_characters pc ON p.player_id = pc.player_id;

external_knowledge:
; The term "damage" refers to any negative effect on a ship, as described in the event impact table; 
; The player with the ship that has the highest damage count is considered the top player; 
; The total credits earned by a player are calculated by summing up their credits from all game dates.

sql:
SELECT player_id, MAX(level) AS max_level
FROM player_progress
GROUP BY player_id;
